{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hallow Maze is a 2.5D metroidvania, with a fast and fluid combat style.The visual style is hand-painted and the artistic style is dark gothic fantasy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will have to transform into creatures and use the power of tools to slay enemies, solve puzzles and discover the truth hidden in the depths of the earth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508560/extras/2captura.png?t=1739389880\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game artstyle is  hand painted carefully desinged in a 2-5D world. Using the best mechanics of the metroidvania genre that we thought were important both to problem solving and combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508560/extras/1captura.png?t=1739389880\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The combat is fast paced, fluid and full of tools that adapt to the playstyle of the player.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508560/extras/5captura.png?t=1739389880\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The highlight of the game are the bosses, difficult fights in which you should use all your arsenal and skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508560/extras/3captura.png?t=1739389880\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508560/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739389880","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.